most of the windows

4
00:00:26,247 --> 00:00:27,840
have been barricaded
with furniture.

5
00:00:28,416 --> 00:00:32,580
But if someone really wanted to,
they could easily break through.

6
00:00:33,121 --> 00:00:37,957
It's better than nothing.
Let's go to the first floor.

7
00:00:38,493 --> 00:00:40,461
Do you know how to shoot?

8
00:00:40,628 --> 00:00:42,323
Y-Yeah. Probably.

9
00:00:43,231 --> 00:00:44,596
I'm going, too.

10
00:00:47,635 --> 00:00:49,125
I have to go, too.

11
00:00:50,104 --> 00:00:52,334
It would be bad if something
were to happen to you.

12
00:00:52,840 --> 00:00:56,674
You need to survive and
tell the world the truth.

13
00:01:08,923 --> 00:01:11,756
Wim, stay in the room.

14
00:01:12,360 --> 00:01:14,727
If something
happens to you...

15
00:01:15,229 --> 00:01:18,995
It's all right. There's no need to worry.
A strong ally is coming to save us.

16
00:01:19,801 --> 00:01:20,427
Really?

17
00:01:20,668 --> 00:01:22,136
Yeah, really.

18
00:01:22,870 --> 00:01:26,602
He comes to save us
whenever we're in danger.

19
00:01:27,475 --> 00:01:31,503
He never let's evil go unpunished.
He's the Magnificent Steiner.

20
00:03:11,746 --> 00:03:13,043
Now! Run!

21
00:03:17,719 --> 00:03:19,187
Take the path through
the woods to the north!

22
00:03:24,459 --> 00:03:27,827
