I'd like to ask you...

28
00:03:41,042 --> 00:03:45,240
Do you know Bonaparta.. .
no.. .Klaus Poppe?

29
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:46,647
Poppe?

30
00:03:47,181 --> 00:03:50,151
Ah. He's the owner
of the Hotel Versteck.

31
00:04:20,014 --> 00:04:21,379
What are you doing there?

32
00:04:25,019 --> 00:04:27,147
Relax. I'm on your side

33
00:04:31,926 --> 00:04:36,420
I ran away in a panic.
But the town is full of corpses.

34
00:04:37,565 --> 00:04:39,556
I don't know where
I should run to.

35
00:04:40,568 --> 00:04:41,558
Where did you run from?

36
00:04:42,236 --> 00:04:45,536
H-He's giving orders
from his room.

37
00:04:45,840 --> 00:04:47,365
I heard.

38
00:04:48,075 --> 00:04:48,701
He?

39
00:04:49,110 --> 00:04:50,134
Roberto!

40
00:04:50,711 --> 00:04:53,737
I thought it was strange that he kept
coming and going from his room!

41
00:04:54,849 --> 00:04:57,580
Each time, he'd change
his clothes and take a shower.

42
00:04:58,219 --> 00:04:59,778
Where is this Roberto?

43
00:05:00,388 --> 00:05:02,447
A room on the fourth floor
of the Hotel Bergbach.

44
00:05:03,191 --> 00:05:08,288
I ...didn't know he was
that sort of person. I...

45
00:05:15,269 --> 00:05:19,763
Listen. Everyone's hiding
in Hotel Versteck.

46
00:05:20,775 --> 00:05:22,174
Can you get there
by yourself?

47
00:05:22,243 --> 00:05:25,008
B-By myself? I'm scared.

48
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:26,478
Now, get up.

49
00:05:26,547 --> 00:05:27,742
I-I'm scared.

50
00:05:50,304 --> 00:05:51,635
Dr. Tenma...

51
00:05:53,407 --> 00:05:54,374
Inspector Lunge...

52
00:05:56,310 --> 00:05:59,871
My journey into delusion...
has finally become reality.

53
00:06:01,282 --> 00:06:07,847
The emergence of you marks the end of
following what I thought were delusions.

54
00:06:08,923 --> 00:06:11,324
My duty as a police officer
begins from this point on.

55
00:06:11,926 --> 00:06:13,587
I'm finally going back to work.

56
00:06:15,796 --> 00:06:22,031
Take this girl to the Hotel Versteck.
The person you're after is there.

57
00:06:24,138 --> 00:06:25,970
Franz.. .Bonaparta...

58
00:06:31,646 --> 00:06:33,705
Inspector Lunge,
where are you going?

59
00:06:35,416 --> 00:06:37,384
I told you, didn't I?
To work...

60
00:06:39,020 --> 00:06:40,181
Let's talk when I get back.

61
00:06:40,821 --> 00:06:42,448
There're a lot of things
I want to ask you about.

62
00:06:47,295 --> 00:06:48,626
Dr. Tenma...

63
00:06:52,033 --> 00:06:53,091
I'm sorry.

64
00:07:03,377 --> 00:07:04,640
Are you all right, Nina?

65
00:07:05,446 --> 00:07:06,743
My memory...

66
