Huh?

77
00:08:32,800 --> 00:08:34,962
I said, "Where's Roberto?"

78
00:08:45,613 --> 00:08:47,741
Stand up. Walk.

79
00:08:48,215 --> 00:08:51,082
I can't take it anymore.
There are dead bodies everywhere.

80
00:08:51,485 --> 00:08:53,749
I'll go crazy here.

81
00:08:54,288 --> 00:08:57,690
Then we've got to get to
Hotel Versteck as soon as possible.

82
00:08:57,792 --> 00:08:59,351
No!

83
00:09:47,141 --> 00:09:49,838
Open your eyes, Erika.

84
00:09:51,612 --> 00:09:54,479
Please... Erika...

85
00:09:55,583 --> 00:09:57,176
She's your wife?

86
