Give me your gun ! I'm going to
gun down the guy who shot Erika!

89
00:10:14,101 --> 00:10:19,369
Give me the gun right now!
He destroyed our happiness.

90
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,430
I'm going to...

91
